All of Alexandria now watches with great anticipation, eager to see if the unenhanced warrior will usher in a revolutionâ”€or if the Tyrant's reign will rage on.
Instancecontenttextdata_40727_Text: Even I felt that! Can't afford to be careless, now!
Instancecontenttextdata_40728_Text: A direct hit! But they're still standing!
Instancecontenttextdata_40732_Text: Once again they slip beyond their opponent's reach!
Instancecontenttextdata_40734_Text: And they're down! Can they recover from this?
Instancecontenttextdata_44100_Text: At long last, the decisive match against the grand champion!
Instancecontenttextdata_44101_Text: Will the challenger triumph and seize the Tyrant's throne?
Instancecontenttextdata_44104_Text: It's Tyranny Time, folks! He knows no mercy, and he's never tasted defeat!
Instancecontenttextdata_44108_Text: I beg your pardon? What is he going to do with all those weapons?
Instancecontenttextdata_44109_Text: Absolute brutality! The champion's power is unmatched!
Instancecontenttextdata_44114_Text: Such ferocity! The champion is ruthless indeed!
Instancecontenttextdata_44120_Text: What a display of power! He's unleashed the full might of the behemoth!
Instancecontenttextdata_44122_Text: Oh, he's split the ring in half! We're going to need urgent repairs!
Instancecontenttextdata_44124_Text: And now he's thrown the ring! What absurd strength!
Instancecontenttextdata_44125_Text: Ahem, the ring shall presently be restored.
Instancecontenttextdata_44127_Text: 'Tis a clash between feral pride and mortal resolve! Either side could come out on top!
